<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #222;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 12px 0;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
    }
    p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>We received a request to verify your account. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete the verification process:</p>
    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
    <p>This code will expire in <strong>2 minutes</strong>. If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Tour Management System. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
